abstract: Nico Rosberg wins pole position for Brazilian Grand Prix auto race.
lead_paragraph: Nico Rosberg won the pole position for Sunday’s Brazilian Grand Prix, edging his Mercedes teammate Lewis Hamilton, who has already clinched the Formula One season title.
